name: Fresh Fitness: Pound Rockout Workout
description: Move to the beat you create at Pound Rockout Workout, every other Tuesday at the Sports Courts. This funk-filled full body workout is designed for all ages and abilities, and will help you tone up and rock on!

name: Movie Night: Cloudy with a Chance of Meatballs
description: Gather on the QuikTrip Great Lawn for a Movie Night presented by Cox! The first summer film in the Cox Movie Night Series is family favorite, “Cloudy with a Chance of Meatballs.” The film will begin at 7:30 p.m. on Wednesday, June 19th. Don’t forget your lawn chair or blankets!

name: Caribbean Vibes
description: Gathering Place is bringing the island state of mind to Tulsa with Caribbean Vibes, a reggae carnival! Catch tropical waves at a day packed full of Caribbean music, dance, food and more dancing. Get a taste of the islands with dishes from local Caribbean restaurants and live performances by Mykal Rose + Sly & Robbie, Reggae Angels, The Stylees and more! Caribbean Vibes will be a day in paradise at the Park!

name: 90's and 2000's Party
description: The hottest party ever! Let's go back in time.
